<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{clientName}} - Guest Experience Platform Proposal</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: letter portrait;
      margin: 0.5in;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #2d3748;
      background: white;
    }

    .page {
      width: 7.5in;
      margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
      background: white;
      page-break-after: always;
    }

    .header {
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #FF6B35;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #FF6B35;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .header-right {
      text-align: right;
      color: #2d3748;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .client-box {
      background: #FFF5F0;
      border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .client-box h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .client-box p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #4a5568;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .usd-badge {
      background: #dbeafe;
      color: #1e40af;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 16px 0;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin: 20px 0 8px 0;
    }

    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .packages {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .package {
      border: 3px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .package.recommended {
      border-color: #2563eb;
    }

    .package-header {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .package.recommended .package-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
      color: white;
    }

    .package:not(.recommended) .package-header {
      background: #f8fafc;
    }

    .badge {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .package:not(.recommended) .badge {
      background: #dbeafe;
      color: #1e40af;
    }

    .package-name {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .package:not(.recommended) .package-name { color: #2d3748; }

    .package-price {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .package:not(.recommended) .package-price { color: #2d3748; }

    .package-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .package:not(.recommended) .package-desc { color: #64748b; }

    .package-body { padding: 20px; }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #2d3748;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .price-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .price-row-label { color: #475569; }
    .price-row-value { font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; }

    .note {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #64748b;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .optional-box {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border: 2px dashed #f59e0b;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .optional-box .section-title { color: #92400e; }

    .features-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }

    .features-list li {
      padding: 6px 0 6px 20px;
      position: relative;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .features-list li::before {
      content: "✓";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #10b981;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* PAGE 2-4 STYLES */
    .content-section { margin-bottom: 24px; }

    .content-section h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .bullet-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }

    .bullet-list li {
      padding: 6px 0 6px 18px;
      position: relative;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .bullet-list li::before {
      content: "•";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .info-box {
      background: #eff6ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }

    .info-box strong {
      color: #1e40af;
      font-size: 13px;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .info-box p {
      color: #1e3a8a;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .text-section {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .text-section strong {
      color: #1e293b;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .orange-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #FF8555 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .orange-box h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: white;
    }

    .orange-box p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .stat-badge {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .feature-box {
      background: white;
      border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .feature-box h3 {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .feature-box p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .arrow-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }

    .arrow-list li {
      padding: 5px 0 5px 20px;
      position: relative;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .arrow-list li::before {
      content: "→";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #FF6B35;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .arrow-list strong { color: #1e293b; }

    .cta-box {
      background: #FFF5F0;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .cta-box h4 {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .cta-box p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #475569;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    @media print {
      body {
        print-color-adjust: exact;
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- PAGE 1: PRICING -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">nutmeg</div>
    </div>

    <div class="client-box">
      <h2>Prepared For: {{clientName}}</h2>
      <p><strong>Project:</strong> Guest Experience Platform Proposal</p>

      {{#if (eq vertical "other")}}
        <p>Comprehensive wayfinding and AI-powered guest engagement solution tailored to your venue.</p>
      {{else}}
        <p>Comprehensive wayfinding and AI-powered guest engagement solution tailored for {{verticalLabel}} operations.</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="usd-badge">ALL PRICING IN USD</div>

    <h1>Platform Packages</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Choose the solution that best enhances your guest experience</p>

    <div class="packages">

      {{!-- LEFT CARD --}}
      {{#if showBundleCards}}
        <div class="package recommended">
          <div class="package-header">
            <div class="badge">RECOMMENDED</div>
            <div class="package-name">Complete Platform</div>
            <div class="package-price">{{fmt.bundleTotal}}</div>
            <div class="package-desc">Maps ({{mapsCount}}) + AI Chatbot</div>
          </div>

          <div class="package-body">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">INTERACTIVE WAYFINDING MAPS ({{mapPlanName}})</div>
              {{#each maps}}
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">{{this.name}}</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{../fmt.mapUnitPrice}}</span>
                </div>
              {{/each}}
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">AI CHATBOT</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Annual Subscription</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">*Based on {{fmt.attendance}} visitors, {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} inquiry ratio, {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest</div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">IMPLEMENTATION & ONBOARDING</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">One-Time Setup Fee</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.setupFee}}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">Includes training, setup, and dedicated support</div>
            </div>

            <div class="optional-box">
              <div class="section-title">OPTIONAL ADD-ONS</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Custom Illustrations</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">$1,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Additional Map Languages</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">$500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">One-time fees, pricing varies by requirements</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {{else}}
        {{#if showMapsOnlyCard}}
          <div class="package recommended">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">RECOMMENDED</div>
              <div class="package-name">Maps Only</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.mapsOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">{{mapPlanName}} ({{mapsCount}} maps)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">WHAT'S INCLUDED ({{mapPlanName}})</div>
                {{#each maps}}
                  <div class="price-row">
                    <span class="price-row-label">{{this.name}}</span>
                    <span class="price-row-value">{{../fmt.mapUnitPrice}}</span>
                  </div>
                {{/each}}
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">One-Time Setup Fee</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.setupFee}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">CORE FEATURES</div>
                <ul class="features-list">
                  {{#each mapPlanFeatures}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                  {{/each}}
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="package recommended">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">RECOMMENDED</div>
              <div class="package-name">AI Chatbot</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.aiOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">AI-powered guest engagement</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">AI CHATBOT</div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Annual Subscription</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="note">*Based on {{fmt.attendance}} visitors, {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} inquiry ratio, {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      {{/if}}

      {{!-- RIGHT CARD --}}
      {{#if showBundleCards}}
        <div class="package">
          <div class="package-header">
            <div class="badge">ESSENTIAL</div>
            <div class="package-name">AI Chatbot Only</div>
            <div class="package-price">{{fmt.aiOnlyTotal}}</div>
            <div class="package-desc">AI-powered guest engagement</div>
          </div>
          <div class="package-body">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">WHAT'S INCLUDED</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Annual Subscription</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">*Based on {{fmt.attendance}} visitors, {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} inquiry ratio, {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest</div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">CORE FEATURES</div>
              <ul class="features-list">
                <li>Works in any language with automatic translation</li>
                <li>Indexed with your information as the source of truth</li>
                <li>Answers operational questions instantly</li>
                <li>Multi-channel integration (WhatsApp, Instagram, SMS)</li>
                <li>Conversation logging for insights and optimization</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {{else}}
        {{#if showAiOnlyCard}}
          <div class="package">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">ESSENTIAL</div>
              <div class="package-name">AI Chatbot</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.aiOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">AI-powered guest engagement</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">USAGE ASSUMPTIONS</div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Expected Conversations</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.expectedConversations}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Expected Cost</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.expectedCost}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Margin Ratio</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.marginProfitRatio}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Quoted Price</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="package">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">ESSENTIAL</div>
              <div class="package-name">Maps Only</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.mapsOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">{{mapPlanName}} ({{mapsCount}} maps)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">WHAT'S INCLUDED</div>
                {{#each maps}}
                  <div class="price-row">
                    <span class="price-row-label">{{this.name}}</span>
                    <span class="price-row-value">{{../fmt.mapUnitPrice}}</span>
                  </div>
                {{/each}}
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">One-Time Setup Fee</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.setupFee}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">CORE FEATURES</div>
                <ul class="features-list">
                  {{#each mapPlanFeatures}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                  {{/each}}
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      {{/if}}

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 2 -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="content-section">
      <h3>Interactive Maps - Core Capabilities</h3>
      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Custom-designed interactive maps for your venue(s)</li>
        <li>Wait time management where applicable</li>
        <li>Location CMS for managing pins and POIs</li>
        <li>Multi-language capability (optional add-on)</li>
        <li>Guest analytics and engagement insights (plan-dependent)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h3>AI Chatbot - Your 24/7 Digital Employee</h3>
      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Works in any language with automatic translation</li>
        <li>Indexed with your venue information as the source of truth</li>
        <li>Answers operational questions instantly - hours, pricing, policies, attraction details</li>
        <li>Drastically reduces phone call volume to your staff</li>
        <li>Multi-channel integration (WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, SMS)</li>
        <li>Complete conversation logging for insights and optimization</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>SMS Messaging:</strong>
      <p>SMS messaging fees are not included in this quote. Twilio service fees will be applied per message based on actual usage volume.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <div class="text-section">
        <strong>Agreement Terms</strong>
        This proposal is provided for {{clientName}}. All pricing is in US Dollars (USD) and valid for {{validityDays}} days from {{preparedDate}}.
      </div>

      <div class="text-section">
        <strong>Usage Assumptions</strong>
        Pricing is based on estimated annual visitation of {{fmt.attendance}} guests with a {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} chatbot inquiry ratio and average of {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest.
      </div>

      <div class="text-section">
        <strong>Questions About This Proposal?</strong>
        <strong>Website:</strong> www.nutmeg.io<br>
        Contact us to discuss this proposal, feature details, or implementation timeline.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 3 -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">nutmeg</div>
    </div>

    <div class="header-right" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Proposal for: {{clientName}}</div>

    <h1>Why Nutmeg for {{clientName}}</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Purpose-built to maximize guest engagement and drive revenue opportunities</p>

    <div class="orange-box">
      <h3>Web-Based Platform = Higher Adoption</h3>
      <p>Mobile apps average less than 3% adoption. Our web-based platform achieves 50%+ adoption rates, meaning more guests engaging with your content, finding attractions faster, and making purchases.</p>
      <div class="stat-badge">17x More Guests Engaged</div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Custom Interactive Wayfinding</h3>
      <p>Our team works with you to create stunning, on-brand maps that guide guests through your venue while driving engagement with revenue-generating opportunities.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>Unlimited customizable pins</strong> - highlight attractions, food venues, retail, events</li>
        <li><strong>Wait time tools</strong> - help guests plan their day and reduce friction</li>
        <li><strong>Geo-fenced marketing</strong> - targeted messages at the right moments (plan-dependent)</li>
        <li><strong>Multi-language support</strong> - serve diverse guests (additional languages are an extra fee)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>AI Chatbot: Your Tireless Digital Employee</h3>
      <p>More than a chatbot - it's an always-on team member that serves as the definitive source of truth about your venue, answering questions instantly and providing peace of mind to your guests.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>Source of truth</strong> - trained on your information, policies, hours, and offerings</li>
        <li><strong>Never takes a break</strong> - operates 24/7, 365 days a year</li>
        <li><strong>Answers operational questions fast</strong> - hours, pricing, requirements, what to bring</li>
        <li><strong>Works in any language</strong> - no language barriers for international guests</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 4 -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Maximize Guest Engagement & Revenue</h3>
      <p>{{clientName}} can benefit from increased guest engagement that drives revenue through food & beverage, retail, and premium experiences.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>No app download barrier</strong> - every guest can access instantly via web browser</li>
        <li><strong>Higher adoption</strong> - means more eyes on your revenue opportunities</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics dashboard</strong> - understand guest flow and optimize engagement (plan-dependent)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Dedicated Support & Partnership</h3>
      <p>You're not just getting software - you're getting a partner committed to your success.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>Designated key account manager</strong> - single point of contact</li>
        <li><strong>Comprehensive onboarding & training</strong> - ensure your team is confident and capable</li>
        <li><strong>Ongoing optimization</strong> - continuous improvement over time</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h4>Ready to Transform Guest Experience at {{clientName}}?</h4>
      <p><strong>Website:</strong> www.nutmeg.io</p>
      <p>Let's schedule a demo tailored to {{clientName}}'s needs and discuss how Nutmeg can drive engagement and revenue.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>